ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectLewisporte Chamber of Commerce (Newfoundland) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the LEWISPORTE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Newfoundland, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the town of Lewisporte to Norris Arm North, Norris Arm South, Lewisporte, Laurenceton, Porterville, Brown's Arm, Stanhope, Embree, Little Burnt Bay, Michael's Harbour, Campbellton, Comfort Cove-Newstead, Loon Bay, Baytona, Birchy Bay and Boyd's Cove.
